{"tid":2013370,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"搵工除咗睇求職網，記得睇埋以下嘅網！","createTime":"2020-05-12T09:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T11:30:57.000Z","uid":50162,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b1edf6d5f5d2d0ff4347461c45ff44d00b7f66","tid":2013370,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"1.<br />\n<a href=\"https://david.co/job.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdavid.co%2Fjob.php&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=6c08da7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://david.co/job.php</a><br />\ncheck吓間公司出job ad出得有幾密，輸入e.g.<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">HR Assistant, Microware</code></pre><br />\n不過個網有時都會有漏網之魚，所以建議喺job description度抽一句出嚟quote起再Google吓，順便又可以知道間公司有冇抄其他公司嘅job ad，e.g.<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&quot;Build up and maintain a good network with other professional organisations so as to acquire new technologies and create synergy&quot;</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n2.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkinterview.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkinterview.com%2F&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=14fe71d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkinterview.com/</a><br />\n睇吓人地點comment間公司<br />\ne.g. <a href=\"https://www.hkinterview.com/?q=467blacklist-19rubbishjob-hongkong-company.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkinterview.com%2F%3Fq%3D467blacklist-19rubbishjob-hongkong-company.html&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=40c34758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkinterview.com/?q=467blacklist-19rubbishjob-hongkong-company.html</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">(NOW TV即PCCW MEDIA) DATA ANALYST &ndash; CRM MARKETING SPECIALIST 唔怪得個個月都出job ad請人, 入面地獄嚟, 上司同事惡頂, 有返工冇收工, 一來turnover rate太高變相一個頂n個, 二來做完都唔敢走, 個個鬥遲走, 諗住做完嘢走人第二日會畀人照肺兼增加workload, 假設您超乎常人超熬得都好, 試用期內呢間垃圾都一定會迫人走, 一個月都好盡下, 難怪個個月都要請人, 總之就係一份玩死人嘅垃圾工!</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n3. <a href=\"https://stealjobs.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstealjobs.com&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=231e3446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stealjobs.com</a><br />\n又係睇吓人地點comment間公司<br />\ne.g. <a href=\"https://stealjobs.com/icba-asia-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%b7%a5%e5%95%86%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%ef%bc%88%e4%ba%9e%e6%b4%b2%ef%bc%89aml-assistant-manager-%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstealjobs.com%2Ficba-asia-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e5%2595%2586%25e9%258a%2580%25e8%25a1%258c%25ef%25bc%2588%25e4%25ba%259e%25e6%25b4%25b2%25ef%25bc%2589aml-assistant-manager-%25e6%2594%25b6%25e5%2585%25a5%2F&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=2c15c240\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://stealjobs.com/icba-asia-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e5%b7%a5%e5%95%86%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8c%ef%bc%88%e4%ba%9e%e6%b4%b2%ef%bc%89aml-assistant-manager-%e6%94%b6%e5%85%a5/</a><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">&ldquo;Unhappy.\nOnce the MLRO knows you&rsquo;re knowledgeable/a threat to him, you will be suppressed. All knowledgeable colleagues have left the bank, [redacted]\n[redacted].&ldquo;&ndash; Anonymous &ndash; 23.7.2017</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e2ca4c19ad4376e94f2b56493148f05b1cbbe0d5","tid":2013370,"uid":82553,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"仲有glassdoor"},{"pid":"42de65eba1cf7f8790c8e17dea75d4d5a6016ab2","tid":2013370,"uid":47374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"34351663a7befc035338250293324f0019e8f25f","tid":2013370,"uid":50162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T09:34:59.000Z","msg":"歡迎各位提供更多網站！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990189861368ef1edf52c5424e2980eb36db